      "title": "Answer Bandula as Minister of Education",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Transport, Highways and Media Minister Bandula Gunawardena has been appointed Minister of Education by President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa.",
        "Education Minister Susil Premajayantha has been appointed Minister of Education by President Bandula Gunawardena as he has gone abroad on an official visit.",
        "Bandula Gunawardena, Minister of Transport, Highways and Media, served as the Minister of Education from 2005 to 2010."
